[OWNER] — people the owner has named or confirmed. Do **not** record AI guesses or web
lookups here. If a new person comes up and isn't in this file, the agent asks "who's
that?" before assuming.

# people.md — everyone the agent should recognize

> The agent reads this at the start of a conversation and consults it whenever a person
> comes up. Add people as they become relevant — you don't need to front-load your whole
> address book.
>
> 에이전트가 대화 시작 시 읽고, 인물이 언급될 때마다 참조합니다. 관련 있어질 때 추가하면
> 됩니다 — 주소록 전체를 미리 넣을 필요 없습니다.

## Agent behavior

| Situation | Action |
|---|---|
| Conversation starts | read this file, note who's here |
| A person is mentioned | search here first → if absent, ask "who's that?" |
| New person confirmed | add them in the format below |
| New info on existing person | update their entry |
| A client / business contact | store in the relevant domain folder, not here |

## Entry format

```md
## [Name]
- **relationship**: [how they relate to you, one line]
- **context**: [where they show up — which project, which part of life]
- **notes**: [anything the agent should remember]
```

